Equipped creature gets +2/+2 and has protection from multicolored and from non-Equipment colorless sources.
Whenever equipped creature deals combat damage to a player, plunder, then exile the top card of that player's library. Until end of turn, you may play that card. [i](To plunder, create a Treasure token, or sacrifice an artifact to draw a card.)[/i]
